虽然2014年4月风力发电和太阳能组合的峰值发电量达到74％的历史最高水平<ref>thinkprogress.org, [http://thinkprogress.org/climate/2014/05/13/3436923/germany-energy-records/Germany Sets New Record, Generating 74 Percent Of Power Needs From Renewable Energy] {{Wayback|url=http://thinkprogress.org/climate/2014/05/13/3436923/germany-energy-records/Germany |date=20141223063719 }}, 13 May 2014</ref> ，但风力发电量在2014年12月12日达到最高峰，达到562[[千瓦时|GWh]]<ref>RenewEconomy.com.au, Craig Morris, [http://reneweconomy.com.au/2014/new-wind-power-generation-record-in-germany-95439 New wind power generation record in Germany] {{Wayback|url=http://reneweconomy.com.au/2014/new-wind-power-generation-record-in-germany-95439 |date=20160531182417 }}, 16 December 2014</ref>。德国被称为“世界第一大可再生能源经济”<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.renewableenergyworld.com/rea/news/article/2009/04/germany-the-worlds-first-major-renewable-energy-economy?cmpid=WNL-Wednesday-April8-2009 |title=Germany: The World's First Major Renewable Energy Economy |accessdate=2016-10-30 |archive-date=2015-03-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150321035535/http://www.renewableenergyworld.com/rea/news/article/2009/04/germany-the-worlds-first-major-renewable-energy-economy?cmpid=WNL-Wednesday-April8-2009 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>Fraunhofer ISE, [http://www.ise.fraunhofer.de/en/downloads-englisch/pdf-files-englisch/data-nivc-/electricity-production-from-solar-and-wind-in-germany-2014.pdf Electricity production from solar and wind in Germany – New record in wind power production] {{WebCite|url=https://www.webcitation.org/6RG21ExIC?url=http://www.ise.fraunhofer.de/en/downloads-englisch/pdf-files-englisch/data-nivc-/electricity-production-from-solar-and-wind-in-germany-2014.pdf |date=20140722131442 |dateformat=iso }}, p.2, 15 December 2014</ref>。

超过23,000台[[风力发动机|风力发动机]]和140万个太阳能[[光伏陣列|光伏系统]]分布在全国各地的357,000平方公里面积上<ref>http://www.wind-energie.de {{Wayback|url=http://www.wind-energie.de/ |date=20161029071341 }}, [http://www.wind-energie.de/en/infocenter/statistiken/deutschland/number-wind-turbines-germany Number of Wind Turbines in Germany] {{Wayback|url=http://www.wind-energie.de/en/infocenter/statistiken/deutschland/number-wind-turbines-germany |date=20160329000414 }}, 2012</ref><ref>Fraunhofer ISE [http://www.ise.fraunhofer.de/en/publications/veroeffentlichungen-pdf-dateien-en/studien-und-konzeptpapiere/recent-facts-about-photovoltaics-in-germany.pdf Recent Facts about Photovoltaics in Germany, p.5] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ise.fraunhofer.de/en/publications/veroeffentlichungen-pdf-dateien-en/studien-und-konzeptpapiere/recent-facts-about-photovoltaics-in-germany.pdf |date=20161222125030 }}, 16 October 2014</ref>。截至2011年，德国联邦政府正在制定一项增加[[可再生能源商业化|可再生能源商业化]]的新计划<ref name=BMU2011_2>{{cite web|url=http://www.erneuerbare-energien.de/inhalt/46959/3860/|title=100% renewable electricity supply by 2050|publisher=[[Federal_Ministry_for_Environment,_Nature_Conservation_and_Nuclear_Safety|Federal Ministry for Environment, Nature Conservation and Nuclear Safety]]|date=26 January 2011|accessdate=4 June 2011|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110509143651/http://www.erneuerbare-energien.de/inhalt/46959/3860/|archive-date=2011-05-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，特别关注[[海上风电场|海上风电场]]<ref name=Spiegel>{{cite web|url=http://www.spiegel.de/international/germany/0,1518,752791,00.html|title=Will Nuke Phase-Out Make Offshore Farms Attractive?|first=Stefan|last=Schultz|date=23 March 2011|work=[[Spiegel_Online|Spiegel Online]]|accessdate=26 March 2011|archive-date=2012-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120210090055/http://www.spiegel.de/international/germany/0,1518,752791,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一个主要的挑战是发展足够的电力网络能力，将北海生产的电力传输给该国南部的大型工业消费者<ref name="ReferenceA">The [[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]] Online, 24 April 2012</ref>。

根据官方数字，2010年可再生能源行业雇用了370,000人，特别是在中小型公司。与2009年（约339,500个工作）相比，这一数字增加了约8％，并且是2004年（160,500）的两倍多。 其中约三分之二的工作被归功于{{le|德国可再生能源法案|German Renewable Energy Sources Act}}<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.erneuerbare-energien.de/files/english/pdf/application/pdf/broschuere_ee_zahlen_en_bf.pdf |title=Renewable Energy Sources in Figures - National and International Development |access-date=2016-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120302094445/http://www.erneuerbare-energien.de/files/english/pdf/application/pdf/broschuere_ee_zahlen_en_bf.pdf |archive-date=2012-03-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.worldwatch.org/node/5430 |title=Germany Leads Way on Renewables, Sets 45% Target by 2030 |access-date=2016-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131202235004/http://www.worldwatch.org/node/5430 |archive-date=2013-12-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

{{le|德国能源转型|Energiewende in Germany}}（{{lang-de|Energiewende}}），指出了2011年[[能源政策|能源政策]]的重大变化。这一术语包括政策从需求到供应的重新定位，以及从集中式向[[分散式發電|分布式发电]]（Distributed Generation）的转变（例如，在非常小的[[热电联产|热电联产]]单位生产热能和电力），应该用节能措施和提高效率取代过度生产和可避免的能源消耗。

